### Create UI Field with Custom React Components

Source: https://github.com/payloadcms/payload/blob/main/tools/claude-plugin/skills/payload/reference/FIELDS.md

Renders fully custom React components in the admin panel without storing data. Supports Field components for main display and Cell components for list views. Enables advanced UI customization beyond standard field types.

```typescript
import type { UIField } from 'payload'

const uiField: UIField = {
  name: 'customMessage',
  type: 'ui',
  admin: {
    components: {
      Field: '/path/to/CustomFieldComponent',
      Cell: '/path/to/CustomCellComponent', // For list view
    },
  },
}
```

