### Configure Upload Field with Media Relations

Source: https://github.com/payloadcms/payload/blob/main/tools/claude-plugin/skills/payload/reference/FIELDS.md

Define upload fields that reference a media collection with MIME type filtering. Supports required validation and filterOptions to restrict file types during upload.

```typescript
import type { UploadField } from 'payload'

const uploadField: UploadField = {
  name: 'featuredImage',
  type: 'upload',
  relationTo: 'media',
  required: true,
  filterOptions: {
    mimeType: { contains: 'image' },
  },
}
```

